### 9.5.2 Architecture

**IMPORTANT:** Use deck.gl for BOTH heatmap AND Gantt views. Mixing deck.gl + Konva 
causes coordinate sync nightmares during zoom transitions ("jittery" effect kills the demo).

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
